            <h2>How It's Calculated</h2>

            <div class="metric">
                <div class="icon good">✔</div>
                <div class="metric-info">
                    <h3>Attractiveness Ratio</h3>
                    <p>The core of your <strong>Popularity</strong>. It's the percentage of users who Like you versus Dislike you. A higher ratio means a stronger profile.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="metric">
                <div class="icon good">✔</div>
                <div class="metric-info">
                    <h3>Match Rate & OTMs</h3>
                    <p>The heart of <strong>Engagement</strong>. We reward you for sending likes that lead to matches and for making a bold first move with OTMs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="metric">
                <div class="icon bad">❌</div>
                <div class="metric-info">
                    <h3>Ghosting Rate</h3>
                    <p>The biggest penalty to your <strong>Engagement</strong> score. Getting a match and never sending a message hurts your score significantly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="metric">
                <div class="icon bad">❌</div>
                <div class="metric-info">
                    <h3>Reports & Blocks</h3>
                    <p>This defines your <strong>Safety</strong> score. Being reported or blocked by other users has a major negative impact and will cap your overall Daaymn Score, no matter how popular you are.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

